# TypeScript

Follow the `clean-typescript` skill (`.cursor/skills/clean-typescript/SKILL.md`).

- Strict mode, no `any` — use `unknown` + narrow or types in `src/lib/def/`
- `import type` for type-only imports
- `.server.ts` = server-only; `.svelte.ts` = runes; `.test.ts` = colocated Vitest
- Types live in `src/lib/def/` — no logic there
